<home-ribbon>Privacy Policy</home-ribbon>

<home-section>
<ul>
<li>The ringgaard.com site does not use ANY <a href="/kb/Q178995">cookies</a> for users.</li>
<li>The site keeps a standard  <a href="/kb/Q5153426">NCSA combined web log</a> of all requests to the site.</li>
<li>The web log is used for standard web traffic measurements and for detecting spam, abuse, and attacks.</li>
<li>Web logs are not shared with anyone outside the organization.</li>
<li>IP addresses that abuse the site will be blocked without further notice.</li>
<li>All URLs for external references use <em>noreferrer</em> so the sites you navigate to are not informed about where you came from.</li>
<li>All trafic between you and ringgaard.com is encrypted (<a href="/kb/Q44484">HTTPS</a>).</li>
</ul>
</home-section>

